{"tid":1569370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知唔知我地既護身符係咩？？","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:25:36.000Z","uid":62011,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94a74a6bb73cb967dd6642111480ad84dc14c149","tid":1569370,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"ABC<br />\n<br />\nanything but Chinazi<br />\n<br />\n你地有冇發現美國國旗旗隊係所有遊行幾乎冇咩出過事？？ 就今日天水圍旗隊面對面對住班狗兩個鐘班狗都冇郁過。<br />\n<br />\n根本政府怕柒出國際，所以唔夠膽亂嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶提下，班藍絲見到外國旗激到扎扎跳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日帶曬其他國家國旗出嚟，唔要支那。"},{"pid":"b1e5365b31c3c561fcaa4ae27ee225db735c076c","tid":1569370,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c032d617a8c190b2b0fe287a82ab03ff0e4e252","tid":1569370,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你個臭街！<br />\n今日死差佬同藍絲又周圍打人呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n聽日九月十五日<br />\n<br />\n12pm 金鐘 英領<br />\n2pm 銅鑼灣東角道 /<br />\n維園  </span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全人類同我出黎！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔係我屌埋你老母呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/915/652/b49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F915%2F652%2Fb49.gif&h=c007be28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div></span>"},{"pid":"5139abbcbb26c284e95d59c72566464727ff35aa","tid":1569370,"uid":257422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n<br />\n雖然表面睇樓主邏輯判斷好似太簡單直接<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但大家思考下，如果一個揸住美國旗既義士俾警察暴力對待、拘捕，<br />\n依個畫面將會幾咁震撼到國際社會既眼球....."},{"pid":"c073186e118f741ec3de981e274aa9d1f099f98a","tid":1569370,"uid":145475,"like":0,"